results.name: Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase 'Pure Platinum Chile Red'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase ‘Pure Platinum Chile Red’ highlights mostly neutral tones on an easy-access version of the performance running shoe. Signature Swoosh branding in a bold scarlet hue enlivens the light grey mesh upper, featuring zippered entry and a no-tie cord lacing system designed to be secured with only one hand. A wider toe box offers plenty of wiggle room, while a plush foam tongue mitigates pressure on the top of the foot. Lightweight cushioning arrives via full-length Nike React midsole with a Zoom Air unit housed in the forefoot.

results.name: React Live TD 'Light Violet Champagne'
results.story: The Nike React Live TD ‘Light Violet Champagne’ showcases pastel hues on a slip-on sneaker that pairs breathable comfort and a cushioned ride. Elastic no-tie laces secure the upper, constructed from a blend of pink textile and open white mesh. Pull tabs at the tongue and heel allow the shoe be easily slipped on and off. The lightweight build is mounted on a sculpted foam midsole, supported underfoot by a rubber outsole for durable traction.

results.name: Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase 'Black White'
Varsity Leather GS 'Particle Grey'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Varsity Leather GS ‘Particle Grey’ showcases a neutral monochromatic on a versatile everyday running shoe made with durability in mind. Grey leather is utilized on the upper, featuring tonal Swoosh branding and toe box perforations for improved ventilation. A classic Nike logo is pressed into the stitched tag that decorates the breathable mesh tongue. The low-top is mounted on a plush foam midsole, supported by lasting rubber in high-wear areas.

results.name: sacai x VaporWaffle 'Dark Iris'
results.story: Designed in coordination with Chitose Abe’s renowned fashion label, the Sacai x Nike VaporWaffle ‘Dark Iris’ showcases sumptuous hues on a retro-inspired silhouette that blends elements from the classic Pegasus 83 with the modern Vaporfly. The reconstructed upper features a purple nylon base with contrasting burnt orange accents on the leather Swoosh and heel tab, marked with dual Nike and Sacai branding. A second printed Swoosh continues a doubled-up theme applied in more literal fashion to the sneaker’s tongues and laces. A partially split foam midsole is reinforced by Nike’s iconic waffle outsole.

results.name: Air Zoom Pegasus 38 'Black'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 ‘Black’ showcases a stealthy monochromatic finish that allows the shoe’s performance benefits to come to the fore. They include an engineered mesh upper built on a new last, yielding a wider toe box for improved comfort. Laces are integrated into a series of interior webbing straps for a more personalized fit. The lightweight build is supported by tooling carried over from the Pegasus 37, which combines full-length React foam cushioning with a springy Zoom Air unit in the forefoot.

results.name: Predator.1 Microbounce 'Demonskin - Black Shock Pink'
results.story: The adidas Predator.1 Microbounce ‘Black Shock Pink’ delivers a lifestyle silhouette that blends performance soccer style with retro cushioning from the brand’s early 2000s archive. The form-fitting Primeknit upper is designed to replicate the look of the Predator Freak.1 soccer cleat, complete with an elastic cuff and faux Demonskin detailing throughout the vamp and midfoot. Springy cushioning is provided by the open-cell structure of adidas’ Microbounce midsole

results.name: Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase 'Summit White Dark Purple Dust'
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase ‘Summit White Dark Purple Dust’ pairs a lightweight and breathable mesh build with open-access functionality. Traditional woven laces are replaced by a set of thin cord laces, easily secured with one hand and integrated into dark violet webbing straps for midfoot lockdown. On the medial side, a zipper runs the length of the eyestay, allowing the shoe to be quickly slipped on and off. The sneaker is placed atop a Nike React foam midsole, featuring a forefoot Zoom Air unit tuned for extra bounce with each step.

results.name: Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 'White Aurora Green'
Wmns Chuck 70 High 'Summer Spirit - Bright Poppy'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck 70 High ‘Summer Spirit’ projects a summer-ready refresh, highlighted by a vintage floral print on an organic canvas upper in Bright Poppy. Traditional winged stitching is applied to the tongue, featuring a throwback Chuck Taylor tag on the interior of the right shoe. Additional branding elements include a circular All Star ankle patch and a 1970s license plate at the back of the midsole, built with raised and shiny rubber sidewalls in keeping with the elevated Chuck 70 aesthetic.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low 'Summer Spirit - Sun and Rainbow'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Summer Spirit’ treats the classic silhouette to a warm-weather makeover. The low-top makes use of an ivory-hued canvas upper with embroidered star and rainbow graphics for a DIY look and feel. Bold pops of color arrive via sun-ray graphics on the custom sockliner in pink, yellow and red. The lace-up is mounted on a towering platform midsole, featuring lightweight EVA cushioning for a smooth ride.

results.name: Air Zoom Arcadia GS 'Black Pink Foam'
Naomi Osaka x Wmns NikeCourt Air Zoom GP Turbo 'Fierce Purple'
results.story: Made for the championship tennis player, the Naomi Osaka x Nike women’s NikeCourt Air Zoom GP Turbo ‘Fierce Purple’ carries a textile upper equipped with a Dynamic Fit system. The technology eliminates the space between the foot and the shoe, resulting in a supportive, second-skin fit. ‘Empowered’ is printed on the tongue tag, while Naomi’s personal logo adorns the heel. The low-top sits on a tonal foam midsole that works in tandem with a full-length Zoom Air unit stitched directly to the upper. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a herringbone tread designed for hard court surfaces.

results.name: Jordan Zion 1 TD 'Gen Zion'
results.story: The Jordan Zion 1 TD ‘Gen Zion’ delivers a miniaturized version of Zion Williamson’s debut signature shoe in its launch colorway. No-tie laces are integrated into a hook-and-loop eyelet that completely detaches, allowing the shoe to be easily slipped on and off. The two-tone upper, constructed from black mesh with white synthetic leather, sits atop a cushy foam sole unit that offers soft landings for little feet. Metallic gold branding elements include a Jumpman icon on the right tongue and a ZW logo on the left.

results.name: Air Zoom Pegasus 38 Extra Wide 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 Extra Wide ‘Black White’ applies a simple two-tone palette to a performance running shoe built on an accommodating last. White Swoosh branding stands out on a ventilated black mesh upper, secured with an integrated lacing system that delivers a feeling of lockdown. The lightweight and seamless build sits atop a resilient React foam midsole, enhanced with a springy Zoom Air unit nestled under the ball of the foot.

results.name: Flex Runner GS 'Crimson Bliss Metallic Platinum'
Nike Air Force 1 Low Acorn (2021)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘Acorn’ brings back a popular earth-toned colorway of the classic hoops silhouette. The upper combines light tan canvas with leather overlays in a subtle beige finish. The same hue is repeated on the Swoosh and Nike branded woven tongue tag. A standard AF1 cupsole anchors the low-top, complete with encapsulated Nike Air cushioning in the heel. Underfoot, the brown rubber outsole features a traction pattern made for pivoting on the hardwood.

results.name: Air Zoom Pegasus 38 FlyEase Extra Wide 'Black Metallic Silver'
Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 'White Metallic Silver'
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Zoom Pegasus 38 ‘White Metallic Silver’ updates the performance running shoe with a lightweight build stripped of all color. An integrated lacing system secures a breathable mesh upper, built with a plush tongue and a wider toe box for an extra-comfortable fit. A cropped and outlined Swoosh shines in metallic silver on the lateral side. The sneaker rides on a matching white Nike React midsole, fitted with a Zoom Air unit in the forefoot for springy cushioning.

results.name: sacai x VaporWaffle 'Sesame Blue Void'
results.story: The sacai x Nike VaporWaffle ‘Sesame Blue Void’ reunites the Swoosh with the Tokyo-based fashion label helmed by Chitose Abe. Blending elements from the modern Vaporfly and vintage Pegasus runner from 1983, the hybrid silhouette makes use of a khaki textile upper with tonal leather and suede overlays. A blue leather Swoosh is joined by a larger printed Swoosh in contrasting white. Tongues are similarly doubled up, each accented with a woven Nike tag. The sneaker rides on a dual-layered foam midsole, featuring split heel detailing and supported by a classic waffle tread outsole.

results.name: Air Force 1 Low GS 'Just Do It - White Volt'
Chuck Taylor All Star EVA Platform Low GS 'Sunflowers'
Air Max 90 PS 'White Hot Lime'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Air Max 90 PS ‘White Hot Lime’ adds vibrant accents to an otherwise neutral colorway of the retro runner. The upper foregoes traditional mesh construction in favor of an all-leather build, rendered in a soft grey finish with a contrasting black mudguard. Fluorescent green pops land on the signature Swoosh, Nike-branded heel patch and visible Max Air cushioning in the heel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a classic waffled tread that ties back to Nike running heritage.

results.name: Wmns Chuck 70 High 'Summer Spirit - Infinite Lilac'
Nike Air Force 1 High EMB Dodgers
results.story: The Nike Air Force 1 High ‘07 LV8 EMB ‘Dodgers’ features a white leather upper with textile overlays and an adjustable ankle strap in Rush Blue, yielding a familiar two-tone color scheme that calls to mind Los Angeles’ iconic MLB franchise. ‘Nike Sports Specialties’ is displayed on the throwback tongue tag, while the lateral heel is decorated with an oversized Nike wordmark in blue embroidery. The high-top rests on a standard AF1 rubber cupsole with encapsulated Nike Air cushioning in the heel.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High 'The Great Outdoors - Claret Red'
results.story: Inspired by the beauty of the natural world, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘The Great Outdoors’ makes use of a recycled jungle cloth upper in a rich Claret Red hue. On the medial ankle, the circular Converse All Star patch is updated with a subtle mountain-vista graphic. The high-top rests on a standard white rubber midsole, accented with black pinstripe detailing and reinforced by a speckled Grind outsole composed of footwear manufacturing scraps.

results.name: Wmns Flex Experience Run 10 'Black Dark Smoke Grey'
React Live TD 'Grey Fog Game Royal'
results.story: The Nike React Live TD ‘Grey Fog Game Royal’ delivers plush cushioning for growing feet. Open mesh and textile make up the composition of the upper, secured with elastic no-tie laces and a one-piece royal blue cord integrated into the pull tab at the heel. The sock-like build sits atop a bulky foam midsole, featuring sculpted sidewalls redolent of Nike React. Underfoot, durable rubber is placed in high-wear areas for added grip.

results.name: Jordan Zion 1 GS 'Gen Zion'
results.story: The Jordan Zion 1 GS ‘Gen Zion’ presents the launch colorway of Zion Williamson’s debut signature shoe in big kid sizing. Celebrating the athlete’s status as a generational talent, the mid-top carries a black mesh upper with a contrasting white synthetic overlay and a graffiti-like ‘Zion’ print throughout the padded textile collar. Gleaming pops of metallic gold land on branding elements that include a Jumpman icon on the right tongue, a ZW logo on the left, and ‘Zion’ inscribed on the heel tab. The sneaker rides on a full-length foam midsole, supported underfoot by an icy translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Low GS 'Croco Surf'
Air Zoom Pegasus 38 'Pure Platinum Chile Red'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 ‘Pure Platinum Chile Red’ updates the lightweight running shoe with an outlined crimson Swoosh on the lateral side. The oversized branding elements adds a touch of extravagance to a reliable daily runner, featuring a light grey engineered mesh upper with a wider-toe box for an accommodating, comfortable fit. Laces are integrated into interior webbing straps for midfoot lockdown. The sneaker rides on a React midsole borrowed from the Pegasus 37, complete with a responsive Zoom Air unit in the forefoot.

results.name: Jordan 4 Retro University Blue
results.story: The Air Jordan 4 Retro ‘University Blue’ updates the classic silhouette with a suede upper in a familiar hue inspired by Michael Jordan’s UNC alma mater. The bright blue palette is contrasted by a speckled grey finish on the sneaker’s supportive wings and back heel, featuring a raised Jumpman icon in black. Secondary Jumpman branding adorns the woven tongue tag, designed to mimic a jock tag that typically appears on the bottom hem of Jordan jerseys.

results.name: Copa Sense.3 Laceless FG 'White Shock Pink'
Jordan 3 Retro A Ma Maniére (W)
results.story: The A Ma Maniére x women's Air Jordan 3 Retro SP ‘Raised By Women’ treats the iconic silhouette to a premium makeover. The Atlanta-based retailer dresses the mid-top in tumbled white leather, overlaid with soft grey suede at the collar, eyestay, heel and toe. Mismatched Jumpman and A Ma Maniére branding is embroidered on each tongue, featuring a quilted lining that’s repeated on the interior collar. A subtle cream hue is applied to the molded heel panel, decorated with an embossed Nike Air logo, and polyurethane midsole. Violet-colored detailing wraps around the heel, providing a contrasting pop of color.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High 'The Great Outdoors - Sea Salt Blue'
Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Flowery Bugs'
Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Sunset Palms - Orange'
Jordan 4 Retro University Blue (PS)
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Air Jordan 4 Retro PS ‘University Blue’ updates the iconic silhouette with a UNC-inspired palette and a smooth suede build. As a callback to the OG ‘White Cement’ colorway, speckled grey detailing is applied to the TPU wings, Air-infused foam midsole and Jumpman branded heel patch. A second Jumpman can be found on the woven jock tag atop the tongue, modeled after the labeling used on vintage Nike basketball jerseys.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Dramatic Nights - White'
results.story: Inspired by summer travel, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Dramatic Nights’ showcases boarding pass-inspired graphics throughout the white canvas upper. They include a QR code-inspired print on the heel and coded flight information contained within a purple strip of color. Accented with contrasting black piping, the upper rests on a standard white rubber midsole with a purple Converse license plate at the heel. A traditional brown rubber outsole delivers durable traction.

results.name: Wmns Nano X1 Grit 'Black Energy Glow'
Wmns Dunk Low Disrupt 'Sea Glass'
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low Disrupt ‘Sea Glass’ offers a modern, reconstructed take on the vintage silhouette. The all-leather upper pairs a white base with contrasting overlays in a subdued tan finish. A soft pink hue distinguishes the exposed-foam tongue, which combines with a leather pull tab at the heel for a DIY-inspired look. The low-top is mounted on a segmented platform midsole with wraparound stitch detailing. Underfoot, flex grooves in the rubber outsole deliver a smooth ride.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Summer Spirit - Sunflowers'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Summer Spirit’ updates the classic silhouette with a floral print designed with the warm-weather months in mind. The high-top carries an off-white canvas upper entirely covered in brown and yellow sunflowers. Standard Chuck details remain intact, including chrome eyelets, an All Star ankle patch and a reinforced rubber toe cap. Matching white rubber is used on the midsole, accented with contrasting black pinstripes and a Converse license plate.

results.name: Copa Sense.2 FG 'White Shock Pink'
results.story: The adidas Copa Sense.2 FG 'White Shock Pink' features inside-out construction intended to mirror the contours of the foot. The anatomical upper pairs soft white leather with a stretch knit collar in contrasting black. Across the medial side, a foam pod delivers impact absorption and allows the ball to stay close to the foot. The lightweight build is placed atop a two-tone TPU outsole, featuring studded traction designed for firm ground surfaces.

results.name: Run Star Hike High 'Summer Spirit - Bright Poppy'
results.story: The Converse Run Star Hike High ‘Summer Spirit’ spotlights a statement-making floral print on a coated canvas upper in Bright Poppy. The vintage ‘70s-inspired print is joined by standard Chuck details, including chrome eyelets, a reinforced rubber toe cap and a circular All Star ankle patch. It all rides on an exaggerated platform midsole, featuring a color-matched One Star logo on the heel and an aggressive sawtooth tread underfoot.

results.name: Nemeziz.3 TF J 'Tension Tape - Screaming Orange'
Jordan 4 Retro University Blue (TD)
results.story: The Air Jordan 4 Retro TD ‘University Blue’ treats this miniaturized version of the classic silhouette to a vibrant makeover, highlighted by a suede upper in Tar Heel blue. The legacy color scheme is contrasted by speckled grey detailing borrowed from the OG ‘White Cement’ colorway, applied to the foam midsole, decorative wings and Jumpman branded heel tab. Underfoot, the rubber outsole utilizes a herringbone traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: Air Zoom Arcadia SE PS 'Glacier Blue Pink Melon Tint'
Nemeziz.2 FG 'Tension Tape - Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas Nemeziz.2 FG ‘Screaming Orange’ showcases a visually arresting graphic print on a wraparound textile upper inspired by sports taping. Tension Tape is utilized on the V-shaped collar to secure the ankle without sacrificing mobility. A central lacing system yields a custom fit. The sleek silhouette is mounted on a TPU outsole designed for firm ground surfaces, featuring an agility stud configuration for superior traction.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High 'The Great Outdoors - Magma Orange'
results.story: Inspired by the natural world, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘The Great Outdoors’ showcases a sweeping landscape graphic in Magma Orange and Sea Salt Blue. Recycled laces secure a canvas upper lined with recycled polyester and branded with a traditional All Star ankle patch. The high-top sits on a traditional white rubber midsole with black pinstripe detailing and a standard Converse license plate. Underfoot, a speckled regrind outsole offers durable traction.

results.name: Jordan 4 Retro University Blue (GS)
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Air Jordan 4 Retro GS ‘University Blue’ carries a suede upper in a familiar color that nods to Michael Jordan’s alma mater, the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill. The collegiate theme is reinforced with a woven jock tag on the tongue, featuring a design similar to the labeling on throwback Nike basketball jerseys. Speckled grey detailing lands on the sneaker’s supportive wings, PU midsole and molded heel tab, the latter embellished with Jumpman branding.

results.name: Run Star Hike Low 'Summer Denim - Vintage White'
results.story: The Converse Run Star Hike Low ‘Summer Denim’ showcases a subdued palette on a bold interpretation of the classic Chuck low-top. Traditional canvas is replaced by a paneled denim build, featuring a Vintage White finish on the lateral side and darker Egret on the opposite side. The low-top is supported by a towering platform midsole, accented with One Star branding at the heel and reinforced by a two-tone sawtooth outsole in the same neutral shades.

results.name: Wmns Chuck 70 High 'Summer Spirit - Gold Dart'
Predator Freak+ Laceless TF 'Demonskin - Shock Pink'
UNTITL3D CS 'Dramatic Nights - White'
results.story: Inspired by summer nights, the Converse UNTITL3D CS ‘Dramatic Nights’ updates the classic Chuck Taylor with a mid-cut collar and distorted details. The white canvas upper is accented with an embroidered Star Chevron logo on the medial ankle and a circular One Star patch on the opposite side. Contrasting black hits land on the mesh tongue, synthetic heel counter and webbing pull tab. The mid-top rides on a vulcanized rubber midsole with raised and textured sidewalls.

results.name: Chuck 70 High 'The Great Outdoors - Multi'
results.story: Inspired by natural landscapes, the Converse Chuck 70 High ‘The Great Outdoors’ features a multicolored, layered design that reflects the interaction between water and land at different temperatures. Recycled laces sure a canvas upper in Bright Poppy, overlaid with peach-colored ripstop, lime green twill canvas and teal slub canvas. The multi-hued assemblage rides on a contrasting white rubber midsole, supported underfoot by a regrind outsole.

results.name: Wmns Run Star Hike High 'Made With Love - White'
results.story: The Converse women’s Run Star Hike High ‘Made With Love’ delivers a handwritten message on the sneaker’s pristine white canvas upper. Both sides panels are marked with embroidered text that lets the wearer know the kicks are made with love, expressed via an embroidered heart in Bright Poppy. The vibrant hue is repeated on a One Star logo on the back heel, as well as the two-tone sawtooth outsole that underpins the exaggerated platform midsole.

results.name: Copa Sense.3 Sala IN 'White Shock Pink'
results.story: A performance soccer shoe made for indoor play, the adidas Copa Sense.3 Sala IN ‘White Shock Pink’ features an anatomical design built from the inside out. Based on data-mapping technology that tracks where the foot and ball connect, the sock-like upper is constructed from breathable mesh with a soft synthetic leather vamp. The low-profile silhouette rests on a lightweight EVA midsole, supported by a flat gum rubber outsole designed for indoor surfaces.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Low TD 'Allover Metallic Stars - White'
results.story: Built for toddlers, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Low TD ‘Allover Metallic Stars’ features convenient slip-on construction with dual hook-and-loop closure in lieu of conventional laces. The white canvas upper is covered in all-over print made up of multicolor stars in a metallic tint. A webbing pull tab at the heel assists with easy on and off, while a SmartFOAM sockliner delivers cushioned comfort for growing feet. Traditional Chuck details include a reinforced toe cap and a woven Converse All Star tag atop the tongue.

results.name: Run Star Hike High 'Summer Denim - Blue'
results.story: The Converse Run Star Hike High ‘Summer Denim’ applies subtle color blocking to the platform high-top. The sneaker’s side panels, tongue and heel overlay are all constructed from washed denim and finished in varying shades of blue. Accented with a standard All Star ankle patch, the upper is mounted on a raised midsole with color-matched One Star detailing at the heel. Underfoot, a decoupled rubber outsole features an exaggerated tread for superior grip.

results.name: Air Structure Triax 91 'Persian Violet'
results.story: The Nike Air Structure Triax 91 ‘Persian Violet’ brings back an OG colorway of the running shoe that provides plush cushioning with a stabile ride. The upper utilizes a breathable white mesh build with a TPU heel counter and contrasting leather overlays in grey and Persian Violet. A black leather Swoosh decorates the lateral side panel, while energetic pops of Solar Red land on the tongue, heel overlay, and medial-side eyelets and midsole. The latter is crafted from polyurethane with a visible Max Air unit in the heel, all of which is supported by a waffle-tread rubber outsole.

results.name: Nemeziz.3 IN J 'Tension Tape - Screaming Orange'
Chuck 70 High 'The Great Outdoors - Chambray Blue'
results.story: The Converse Chuck 70 High ‘The Great Outdoors’ features a layered design that draws inspiration from natural landscapes, and the ways in which water interacts with land at different temperatures. The upper is constructed from organic canvas in Chambray Blue. A visual thermal effect is achieved by adding wraparound overlays in tan ripstop, blue twill canvas and navy slub canvas. The high-top is mounted on an off-white rubber midsole with the Chuck 70’s standard raised sidewalls.

results.name: Run Star Hike High 'Summer Spirit - Sesame'
results.story: The Converse Run Star Hike High ‘Summer Spirit’ showcases a stylized floral print throughout the Sesame-colored canvas upper. The vintage-inspired design is contrasted by a modern platform midsole, featuring stark white sidewalls and a sawtooth traction pattern underfoot. Color-matched One Star detailing decorates the heel. Additional branding elements include a circular All Star ankle patch and a vintage Converse tag on the interior tongue of the right shoe.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Summer Denim - Denim'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule ‘Summer Denim’ applies a pastel blue finish to a radically reworked version of the classic silhouette. Open heel construction transforms the low-top sneaker into an easy-to-wear slip-on, crafted from washed denim and secured with traditional lace closure. A multicolor floral print is applied the Ortholite sockliner and interior lining, enhancing the shoe’s summery aesthetic.

results.name: X Ghosted.3 TF J 'Shock Pink'
results.story: Offered in kids sizing, the adidas X Ghosted.3 TF J ‘Shock Pink’ updates the turf shoe with a vibrant pink finish. The eye-catching hue is applied to a lightweight mesh upper that provides a snug, sock-like fit, thanks to the addition of a low-cut Clawcollar and a four-way stretch tongue. The streamlined build rides on a cushy EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a lugged rubber outsole specifically designed for play on artificial-turf pitches.

results.name: Nike Lebron 8 Hardwood Classic (2021)
results.story: Replicating the look of an unreleased sample pair that surfaced in 2010, the Nike LeBron 8 ‘HWC’ dresses the retro silhouette in a color scheme inspired by the Cleveland Cavaliers’ throwback jerseys from the late ‘80s. A vibrant royal blue finish is applied to the upper, constructed from a blend of suede and TPU. Contrasting orange accents land on the laces and tongue, embellished with a 3D graphic of LeBron James’ lion logo. The citrus hue is repeated on sneaker’s full-length Max Air unit and rubber outsole.

results.name: One Star Low 'The Great Outdoors - Midnight Clover'
results.story: Celebrating the natural world, the Converse One Star Low ‘The Great Outdoors’ features an abstract landscape-inspired print throughout the upper, constructed from recycled polyester in Midnight Clover. The low-top is accented with One Star branding and placed atop an off-white rubber midsole, stamped with a tonal Converse license plate at the heel. Underfoot, a speckled regrind outsole features a traditional diamond traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Copa Kapitan.2 FG 'White Gold Metallic'
results.story: The adidas Copa Kapitan.2 FG ‘White Gold Metallic’ makes use of a premium K-leather upper designed to mold around the individual contours of the wearer’s foot. The pristine white finish is enlivened with metallic gold branding hits, including stitched three-stripes and a classic adidas logo atop the fold-over tongue. The lace-up sits on a firm-ground TPU outsole, featuring strategically placed studs that deliver optimal stop-and-go traction.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High TD 'Gingham'
One Star Low 'The Great Outdoors - Midnight Navy'
results.story: Celebrating the beauty of the natural world, the Converse One Star Low ‘The Great Outdoors’ features an earthy multicolor print on a sustainable build. Recycled poly-canvas in Midnight Navy makes up the majority of the upper, with exterior branding limited to the signature One Star logo on the quarter panel. The low-top is lined in synthetic leather and mounted on a solid white rubber midsole. Underfoot, a regrind outsole features a traditional diamond tread for reliable grip.
